Package: SurvNPSA
Type: Package
Title: Nonparametric Causal Sensitivity Analysis for Survival Outcomes
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Rui", "Hu", email = "ruihu.cufe@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    SurvNPSA implements a nonparametric causal sensitivity analysis framework for time-to-event data, 
    providing nonparametric bounds and valid inference for survival contrasts, 
    including differences in survival curves and restricted mean survival times (RMST), 
    along with summary metrics to assess the extent of unobserved confounding required to explain away observed causal effects.
